<p class="ql-align-center">院内的雪与民宿的外墙相互映衬着白色</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白雪同样在远处山峦间飞舞着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>千里山间，银装素裹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">群山被“绒装”掩盖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没了踪影</strong></p>
<h1>红叶谷</h1>
