<p class="ql-align-center">近处的亭子、远处的塔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有四周的山峦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加上宛如镜子般的水面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都被白雪覆盖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隐隐约约、朦朦胧胧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201121/af0be11c26214ee982f33cf96c58b241.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
