<p class="ql-align-center">树尖上冒出了朵朵白花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地上是一层白色绒毯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一夜之间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整个山都被埋进了雪里</p>
<h1>龙门山</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201121/f05efeafc0784d34966c620454ee41c3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201121/3eeb7af44547482d8081007269be7943.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201121/ab7a46b8e617459faff7d63c48736990.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201121/eac2ef8e4a174b889931f6b8066b7ed2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201121/0b19835637bc4a0390635083ad060f16.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纷扬的雪花来得悄无声息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>往地上铺，往屋上盖，往树上靠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只看到那白色灰色相交相融</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美得让人失语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>初雪为欢谣，再雪犹喜视</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每一场雪都是大自然的馈赠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它带给我们静谧的好时光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又带给田地来年的好收成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它是冬天里<strong>最特别的礼物</strong></p>
